---
const serif = { fontFamily: "'Instrument Serif', serif" };
const sans = { fontFamily: "'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif" };
---

<div class="min-h-screen bg-off-white text-slate-900" style={sans}>
  <header class="mx-auto flex max-w-7xl items-center justify-between px-6 pt-6 sm:px-10">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
      <div class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-teal-700" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <span class="dm-sans text-xl tracking-tight italic text-slate-950" style={serif}>Axiom</span>
    </div>
    <nav class="hidden items-center gap-8 text-sm md:flex">
      <a href="#product" class="transition-colors hover:text-teal-700">Product</a>
      <a href="#how" class="transition-colors hover:text-teal-700">How it works</a>
      <a href="#tracks" class="transition-colors hover:text-teal-700">Tracks</a>
      <a href="#contact" class="transition-colors hover:text-teal-700">Contact</a>
    </nav>
    <a href="/decision?mode=quotations" class="rounded-full bg-teal-700 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-white transition-opacity hover:opacity-90">
      Start decision
    </a>
  </header>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 pt-14 pb-10 sm:px-10 sm:pt-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
      <div class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-1.5 text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-slate-500">
        <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-teal-700"></span>
        Axiom procurement analyst
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl leading-[1.02] tracking-tight text-slate-950 sm:text-7xl md:text-8xl" style={serif}>
        Procurement decisions
        <br />
        <em class="not-italic text-teal-700">you can defend.</em>
      </h1>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-600 sm:text-lg">
        Compare vendor quotations or explore trusted catalogue options. Axiom normalises inputs,
        discovers decision criteria, weighs tradeoffs, and produces an explainable recommendation.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <a href="/decision?mode=quotations" class="rounded-full bg-teal-700 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white transition-opacity hover:opacity-90">
          Upload quotations
        </a>
        <a href="#tracks" class="rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 transition-colors hover:bg-slate-50">
          Use catalogue
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="relative mx-auto mt-14 w-full max-w-5xl overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-[0_30px_80px_-30px_rgba(15,118,110,0.25)]">
        <video src="/axiom-hero.mp4" autoplay muted loop playsinline class="block w-full" aria-label="Axiom abstract motion identity"></video>
        <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 flex items-end justify-between px-6 py-4 text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-slate-500">
          <span>Study № 01</span>
          <span>Clarity · by design</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="how" class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-24 sm:px-10">
    <div class="mb-14 flex items-end justify-between gap-6">
      <h2 class="max-w-xl text-4xl tracking-tight sm:text-5xl" style={serif}>
        A structured path from inputs to defensible output.
      </h2>
      <div class="hidden text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-slate-500 md:block">How it works</div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid gap-px overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-200 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="bg-white p-8">
        <div class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-slate-500">Step 01</div>
        <div class="mt-4 text-xl text-slate-950" style={serif}>Understand options</div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">Normalise uploaded PDFs into structured vendor facts.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-8">
        <div class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-slate-500">Step 02</div>
        <div class="mt-4 text-xl text-slate-950" style={serif}>Discover priorities</div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">Surface the decision criteria that actually matter.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-8">
        <div class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-slate-500">Step 03</div>
        <div class="mt-4 text-xl text-slate-950" style={serif}>Defend recommendation</div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">Weighted scoring with an explainable tradeoff view.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="tracks" class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 pb-24 sm:px-10">
    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
      <a href="/decision?mode=quotations" class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 transition-colors hover:border-teal-700/40">
        <div class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-slate-500">Track A</div>
        <div class="mt-4 text-2xl text-slate-950" style={serif}>Upload vendor quotations</div>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-md text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
          Normalise uploaded PDFs into structured vendor facts, then score each quote against the same criteria and tradeoffs.
        </p>
        <span class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-teal-700">
          Start with quotations
          <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </span>
      </a>

      <a href="/decision?mode=catalogue" class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 transition-colors hover:border-teal-700/40">
        <div class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-slate-500">Track B</div>
        <div class="mt-4 text-2xl text-slate-950" style={serif}>Use catalogue RAG</div>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-md text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
          Start without quotations. Retrieve relevant vendor context from the catalogue and run it through the same metrics pipeline.
        </p>
        <span class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-teal-700">
          Explore the catalogue
          <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer id="contact" class="border-t border-slate-200">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-10 px-6 py-14 sm:px-10 md:grid-cols-4">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <div class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-teal-700"></div>
          <span class="text-lg italic text-slate-950" style={serif}>Axiom</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-sm text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
          An explainable procurement analyst. Clarity, by design.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-slate-500">Product</div>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="#how" class="hover:text-teal-700">How it works</a></li>
          <li><a href="#tracks" class="hover:text-teal-700">Tracks</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-slate-500">Company</div>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="#contact" class="hover:text-teal-700">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="border-t border-slate-200">
      <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-7xl items-center justify-between px-6 py-5 text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-slate-500 sm:px-10">
        <span>© MMXXVI Axiom</span>
        <span>Clarity · by design</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</div>
